\end_inset

).
\begin_inset Foot
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Seeking to debunk government officials' and mainstream economists' claim
 that the crisis was unforeseen and unforeseeable, 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citet
after "7-9"
key "bezemer2009noone"

\end_inset

identified authors who met four criteria.
 They must have: not only predicted the crisis, but also explained how they
 arrived at their prediction; linked the prediction about a real estate
