\end_inset

 Additionally, most of the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

tribes
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 have inclination to build an edifice of coherent, cumulative research needed
 to address these structural dynamics.
 Instead of building on a common basis, they are more inclined to blaze
 their own trails.
 In the competition to come up with the next new idea or to churn out yet
 another article, there is often a lack of the time or the attention to
 detail needed to study meaningfully something as hidden and complex as
 these dynamics.
 Instead, much as the literature on flexible specialization claims about
 firms making major capital investments in a turbulent economic environment
 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
